The Keiser Report  No. 137
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 12 April 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy report on the murderer of the middle class and how the wealth effect equals the poverty effect. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Jim Rickards of Tangent Capital about the silver, gold, the dollar and quantitative easing.
